-- Anil Ambani's Reliance Power, Reliance Natural to Merge in Share-Swap Deal
-- Anoop Agrawal
-- 2010-07-04T09:00:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-04/reliance-power-reliance-natural-to-merge-in-four-for-one-share-swap-deal.html

          
          
             Reliance Natural Resources Ltd. and
Reliance Power Ltd. agreed to merge in a share-swap agreement.  
 The merger will be carried out through an exchange of one
Reliance Power share for every four Reliance Natural shares
held, according to a Reliance group statement sent by e-mail.  
